165
00:09:17,875 --> 00:09:19,625
Aduhai.

166
00:09:30,250 --> 00:09:33,208
Baiklah. Kita patut buat begini.

167
00:09:33,708 --> 00:09:36,333
Asingkan barang yang kita nak simpan

168
